reviewText: This DVD is a fun thing to own... Have all the aesthetic advantages of a salt water aquarium without the hassle and unavoidable death toll of poor misadapted fish.... Really cool!

For the money, its a good tape.  It's about 45 min of 3 reef areas.  We enjoy using our fish i.d. charts and spotting different fish.  You will see lots of different fish.  Have snorkeled many places and saw a few here I'd  never seen.  There's even two types of sharks.
